data.description: Welcome to the ideal blend of comfort and modern functionality! Step into the heart of the home - a polished white kitchen adorned with stainless steel appliances. Adjacent, enjoy the convenience of a generously-sized office perfect for working from home. Relax in front of the toasty fireplace in the spacious yet cozy living room. Upstairs, a loft offers plenty of built-in storage. Outside, the large fenced-in backyard beckons, providing ample space for outdoor activities and gardening. Plus, Cedar Hill Park is practically your neighbor (1 mile away), the airport's a breezy 15-minute hop, and downtown's just 20-minutes away. Bonus: Bask in the luxury of a brand new rainwater softener, a water filter that's been distilled not once, but twice, an ozone laundry W/D (included), and a top-notch ozone air purifier system that's basically the superhero of your whole house. And let's not forget the cool kids on the block – dual HVAC systems, just 1-2 years young! Open House Sun 1/14 from 2-4.
